 and Dark compete to determine the outcome--one member of the Fellowship of the Ring is revealed as the noble heir to the throne of the Kings of Men. Yet, the sole hope for triumph over evil lies with a brave hobbit, Frodo, who, accompanied by his loyal friend Sam and the hideous, wretched Gollum, ventures deep into the very dark heart of Mordor on his seemingly impossible quest to destroy the Ring of Power.​","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":26.3842,"vote_count":26074,"poster_path":"/rCzpDGLbOoPwLjy3OAm5NUPOTrC.jpg","release_date":"2003-12-17","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/2u7zbn8EudG6kLlBzUYqP8RyFU4.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","original_language":"en"},{"id":18,"adult":false,"title":"The Fifth Element","video":false,"overview":"In 2257, a taxi driver is unintentionally given the task of saving a young girl who is part of the key that will ensure the survival of humanity.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":11.8876,"vote_count":11464,"poster_path":"/fPtlCO1yQtnoLHOwKtWz7db6RGU.jpg","release_date":"1997-05-02","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/bx1W729hyWQqNQoiq9LsX30FBf.jpg","original_title":"Le Cinquième Élément","original_language":"fr"},{"id":24,"adult":false,"title":"Kill Bill: Vol. 1","video":false,"overview":"An assassin is shot by her ruthless employer, Bill, and other members of their assassination circle – but she lives to plot her vengeance.","genre_ids":[28,80],"popularity":16.6569,"vote_count":18600,"poster_path":"/v7TaX8kXMXs5yFFGR41guUDNcnB.jpg","release_date":"2003-10-10","vote_average":7.971,"backdrop_path":"/iffzIhuLAO38Po6sh1s6ZEVwlNL.jpg","original_title":"Kill Bill: Vol. 1","original_language":"en"},{"id":63,"adult":false,"title":"Twelve Monkeys","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2035, convict James Cole reluctantly volunteers to be sent back in time to discover the origin of a deadly virus that wiped out nearly all of the earth's population and forced the survivors into underground communities. But when Cole is mistakenly sent to 1990 instead of 1996, he's arrested and locked up in a mental hospital. There he meets psychiatrist Dr. Kathryn Railly and the son of a famous virus expert who may hold the key to the Army of the 12 Monkeys; thought to be responsible for unleashing the killer disease.","genre_ids":[878,53,9648],"popularity":8.5281,"vote_count":8940,"poster_path":"/gt3iyguaCIw8DpQZI1LIN5TohM2.jpg","release_date":"1995-12-29","vote_average":7.601,"backdrop_path":"/mKIkGoyuR71qz6FdiEiOjxvBQcS.jpg","original_title":"Twelve Monkeys","original_language":"en"},{"id":79,"adult":false,"title":"Hero","video":false,"overview":"During China's Warring States period, a district prefect arrives at the palace of Qin Shi Huang, claiming to have killed the three assassins who had made an attempt on the king's life three years ago.","genre_ids":[18,12,28,36],"popularity":5.4979,"vote_count":2436,"poster_path":"/vxgZto2Cz7ILHAlmRXt50I2brB2.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-19","vote_average":7.508,"backdrop_path":"/jDz6RYN3nKYtlo7J9IMvGoJit7B.jpg","original_title":"英雄","original_language":"zh"},{"id":82,"adult":false,"title":"Miami Vice","video":false,"overview":"A case involving drug lords and murder in South Florida takes a personal turn for undercover detectives Sonny Crockett and Ricardo Tubbs. Unorthodox Crockett gets involved romantically with the Chinese-Cuban wife of a trafficker of arms and drugs, while Tubbs deals with an assault on those he loves.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":3.2016,"vote_count":1916,"poster_path":"/1KGD2g0wOc7WBfHc5G19reLHQxk.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-27","vote_average":6.022,"backdrop_path":"/lV2UQv1qmiZA0tWsVjgFLD6z2uG.jpg","original_title":"Miami Vice","original_language":"en"},{"id":271110,"adult":false,"title":"Captain America: Civil War","video":false,"overview":"Following the events of Age of Ultron, the collective governments of the world pass an act designed to regulate all superhuman activity. This polarizes opinion amongst the Avengers, causing two factions to side with Iron Man or Captain America, which causes an epic battle between former allies.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"popularity":13.608,"vote_count":23762,"poster_path":"/rAGiXaUfPzY7CDEyNKUofk3Kw2e.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-27","vote_average":7.446,"backdrop_path":"/wdwcOBMkt3zmPQuEMxB3FUtMio2.jpg","original_title":"Captain America: Civil War","original_language":"en"},{"id":271205,"adult":false,"title":"The Custodian","video":false,"overview":"Detective James Quinlan has left his alcoholic wife, sprouting a bloom of insecurity, anger and self-motivation within him to expose the corrupt police force that surrounds him. He abandons his straight life to join his partner Detective Church in order to get on the inside of the circle of double-agents. He secretly sides with a reporter and an Internal Affairs lawyer to expose them to the press.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":0.4382,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/3whZKJjrJgXVwNOdHza1IN3Ymov.jpg","release_date":"1994-03-17","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/nPpT0sOJoTVzbGagYoWrhxgQwok.jpg","original_title":"The Custodian","original_language":"en"},{"id":273187,"adult":false,"title":"The Scarehouse","video":false,"overview":"When two friends open a Halloween fun house on Devil's Night it is all fun and games until their former sorority sisters begin to arrive. These six sisters are confronted by their past as the night spins out of control.","genre_ids":[53,27],"popularity":0.3391,"vote_count":55,"poster_path":"/dE6VEAOTvJOu0ER6nkSkfJKxCG2.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-13","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/n6JPhgmFzdYbozKJSa0JTaOmHEO.jpg","original_title":"The Scarehouse","original_language":"en"},{"id":1679,"adult":false,"title":"Godzilla Raids Again","video":false,"overview":"Two fishing scout pilots make a horrifying discovery when they encounter a second Godzilla alongside a new monster named Anguirus. Without the weapon that killed the original, authorities attempt to lure Godzilla away from the mainland. But Anguirus soon arrives and the two monsters make their way towards Osaka as Japan braces for tragedy.","genre_ids":[878,27,28],"popularity":1.2982,"vote_count":322,"poster_path":"/ipU1exHwS04FhdonFXsliOKrr2a.jpg","release_date":"1955-04-24","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/xbKFQCZNK14gp9k6cFCwgp2OCtU.jpg","original_title":"ゴジラの逆襲","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1680,"adult":false,"title":"King Kong vs. Godzilla","video":false,"overview":"The advertising director of Pacific Pharmaceuticals, frustrated with the low ratings of their sponsored TV program, seeks a more sensationalist approach. He orders his staff to Faro Island to capture King Kong for exploitation. As Godzilla re-emerges, a media frenzy generates with Pacific looking to capitalize off of the ultimate battle.","genre_ids":[878,35,12,14,28],"popularity":2.1946,"vote_count":334,"poster_path":"/dmCfyzUl0Ylk8Rpi6dYyWuBrnNr.jpg","release_date":"1962-08-11","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/9H8wGFwKKt2ADRhg2odywTg1NCZ.jpg","original_title":"キングコング対ゴジラ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1573,"adult":false,"title":"Die Hard 2","video":false,"overview":"One year after his heroics in Los Angeles, John McClane is an off-duty cop who is the wrong guy in the wrong place at the wrong time. On a snowy Christmas Eve, as he waits for his wife's plane to land at Washington Dulles International Airport, terrorists take over the air traffic control system in a plot to free a South American army general and drug smuggler being flown into the US to face drug charges. It's now up to McClane to take on the terrorists, while coping with an inept airport police chief, an uncooperative anti-terrorist squad, and the life of his wife and everyone else trapped in planes circling overhead.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":6.7639,"vote_count":6273,"poster_path":"/ybki0UWO3OPhaM6MSniuKC7sy1R.jpg","release_date":"1990-07-03","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/cDtefl7KGnKrDziEUXetMnztvqr